<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />！<delay frames="40" />
今晚就是<delay8 />期待已久的煙火大會囉！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你要注意別錯過囉～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會從19點開始喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我太過期待今晚的煙火大會，<delay20 />
感覺今天時間過得特別慢呢。<delay frames="60" />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />能不能快點到19點啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 28 00 00 00 00"><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
你還記得<delay8 /><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今天是什麼日子吧～？<pageBreak /><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />是煙火大會啦，<delay20 />煙火大會！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />大會會在19點開始，<delay frames="40" />
你可別忘了喔～！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會<delay20 />就快要開始了喔～！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你準備好了嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火大會再一下子就要開始了。<delay frames="40" />
不知道在哪裡能看得最清楚～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />嗯<tag a="110" b="0" />那邊應該不錯喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 27 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />高空煙火已經差不多該發射了吧？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我已經做好萬全準備了，
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />儘管來吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />煙火真是美麗啊～<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />直到現在，<delay8 />腦中都還彷彿留有
煙火在空中爆發的聲響，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="HappyDance" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這次的煙火大會也很棒呢！<10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為一直抬頭仰望高空，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以感覺脖子有點不舒服～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="009" attrib="00 00 00 26 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好～啦，煙火也已經放完了，<delay20 />
去吃點東西填飽肚子吧～<pageBreak /><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看煙火看得太認真，<delay20 />
肚子已經餓扁啦，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />今年最後的煙火大會，<delay frames="40" />
已經結束了嗎<tag a="110" b="0" /><10_4 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我很享受大會喔～！<pageBreak /><anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />如果明年<delay8 />也能跟<tag a="110" b="33" />的大家
一起看煙火就好了～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />煙火真的<delay20 />好漂亮啊～<delay frames="50" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不愧是今年最後的煙火大會，<delay20 />
大家把現場氣氛炒熱到最高點呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 29 00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今年最後的煙火大會真是太棒了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我想好好地觀賞煙火，<delay20 />
所以連眼睛都不敢眨呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>